ivos no estn afectados.&#xa0;Esta vulnerabilidad afecta a Firefox versiones anteriores a 86','Firefox for Android suffered from a time-of-check-time-of-use vulnerability that allowed a malicious application to read sensitive data from application directories. Note: This issue is only affected Firefox for Android. Other operating systems are unaffected. This vulnerability affects Firefox < 86.','NONE'),('CVE-2021-24026','HIGH',9.8,'CRITICAL','HIGH','Una falta de comprobacin de lmites dentro de la tubera de decodificacin de audio para llamadas de WhatsApp en WhatsApp para Android versiones anteriores a v2.21.3, WhatsApp Business para Android versiones anteriores a v2.21.3, WhatsApp para iOS versiones anteriores a v2.21.32 y WhatsApp Business para iOS versiones anteriores a v2. 21.32, podra haber permitido una escritura fuera de lmites','A missing bounds check within the audio decoding pipeline for WhatsApp calls in WhatsApp for Android prior to v2.21.3, WhatsApp Business for Android prior to v2.21.3, WhatsApp for iOS prior to v2.21.32, and WhatsApp Business for iOS prior to v2.21.32 could have allowed an out-of-bounds write.','HIGH'),('CVE-2021-24027','NONE',7.5,'HIGH','HIGH','Un problema de configuracin de cach anterior a WhatsApp para Android versin v2.21.4.18 y WhatsApp Business para Android versin v2.21.4.18, puede haber permitido a un tercero con acceso al almacenamiento externo del dispositivo leer material TLS almacenado en cach','A cache configuration issue prior to WhatsApp for Android v2.21.4.18 and WhatsApp Business for Android v2.21.4.18 may have allowed a third party with access to the devices external storage to read cached TLS material.','NONE'),('CVE-2021-24041','HIGH',9.8,'CRITICAL','HIGH','Una comprobacin de lmites faltante en el cdigo de desenfoque de imgenes anterior a WhatsApp para Android v2.21.22.7 y WhatsApp Business para Android v2.21.22.7 podra haber permitido una escritura fuera de lmites si un usuario enviaba una imagen maliciosa','A missin